        "width": 560,
        "height": 736,
        "content": "## âš™ï¸ Customization\n\n* `Set Daily Limit` node controls the number of free generations\n* You can add:\n\n  * NSFW filtering\n  * Dynamic model selection\n  * `/help` or `/history` commands\n\n---\n\n## ğŸ’¡ Example User Flow\n\n1. User sends:\n\n   ```\n   a dragon flying above New York at night\n   ```\n\n2. Bot replies:\n\n   > **Hereâ€™s your image:**\n   > A crimson dragon soars through moonlit clouds over Manhattan, its wings glowing against the skyline.\n\n> 3. Image is generated and sent\n"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
