        "width": 560,
        "height": 912,
        "content": "\n# ğŸ›  Setup Guide\n\n### 1. ğŸ“² Create a Telegram Bot\n\n* Go to [@BotFather](https://t.me/BotFather)\n* Use `/newbot`, set a name and username\n* Save the **API token**\n\n---\n\n### 2. ğŸ” Connect Telegram API in n8n\n\n* Go to `Credentials > Telegram API`\n* Create new credentials using the token from BotFather\n\n---\n\n### 3. ğŸ“— Create a Google Sheet\n\n* Add a sheet named `Sheet1`\n\n* Use these columns as headers:\n\n  ```\n  user_id | date | query | result_url\n  ```\n\n* Share it with your Google service account or OAuth user\n  (depends on how you authenticate Google Sheets in n8n)\n\n---\n\n### 4. ğŸ”Œ Set Up Credentials in n8n\n\n* **Google Sheets:** OAuth2 or service account\n* **AIMLAPI:** Use your API key in `AI/ML API` credentials\n\n  * Base URL: `https://api.aimlapi.com/v1`\n  * Docs: [docs.aimlapi.com](https://docs.aimlapi.com)\n"
